OL,3,CSurvivors of 'horrendous' medical
OL,4,Cscandals 'ignored' by government
OL,6,FWomen who have been left with severe
OL,7,Fdisabilities and health problems after
OL,8,Fsurviving two of the biggest medical
OL,9,Fscandals in modern history say they
OL,10,Ffeel badly let down and ignored by the
OL,11,Fgovernment.
OL,13,FEngland's Patient Safety Commissioner
OL,14,Fcalled for immediate financial redress
OL,15,Ffor thousands of pregnant women whose
OL,16,Fbabies were born with life long
OL,17,Fdisabilities linked to an epilepsy
OL,18,Fmedication.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
