OL,3,CSurvivors of 'horrendous' medical
OL,4,Cscandals 'ignored' by government
OL,6,FShe also recommended payments for
OL,7,Fpeople who were left in chronic pain
OL,8,Fafter being fitted with pelvic mesh
OL,9,Fimplants. But one year on since the
OL,10,Freport and there has been no action
OL,11,Ffrom the government.
OL,13,FAmong thousands of people impacted by
OL,14,Fthe catastrophic medical failures is
OL,15,FIndira Tailor, a former practice nurse
OL,16,Fwho was forced to give up work because
OL,17,Fof excruciating pain caused by a
OL,18,Fpelvic mesh implant.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
