OL,3,CSurvivors of 'horrendous' medical
OL,4,Cscandals 'ignored' by government
OL,6,FThousands of women reported issues
OL,7,Fafter surgery, with side effects such
OL,8,Fas infection, pelvic pain, difficulty
OL,9,Furinating, pain during sex and
OL,10,Fincontinence reported. Often, these
OL,11,Fwomen were dismissed.
OL,13,F"I was banging my head against a brick
OL,14,Fwall", said Mandy Bridge, a former
OL,15,Fhairdresser who lives with
OL,16,Fdebilitating pain after having
OL,17,Fsurgical mesh implanted in 2015. "I
OL,18,Fwas told 'that can't possibly stick in
OL,19,Fyou'."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
