OL,3,CSurvivors of 'horrendous' medical
OL,4,Cscandals 'ignored' by government
OL,6,F"If you'd examined me you could feel
OL,7,Fit, it was there. To put it in such a
OL,8,Fdeep area, and have no plan how to get
OL,9,Fit out, is horrendous to me. I'd have
OL,10,Fnever had it put in if I'd have known."
OL,12,FThe Patient Safety Commissioner, Dr
OL,13,FHenrietta Hughes, said there is a
OL,14,F"clear case for redress" for thousands
OL,15,Fof women and children affected by mesh
OL,16,Fimplants and sodium valproate.
OL,18,FShe said the Government need to "get
OL,19,Fon with" creating a two-stage
OL,20,Ffinancial redress scheme ` an interim
OL,21,Fscheme and a main scheme.
