OL,4,Cscandals 'ignored' by government
OL,6,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,7,FCare says it is "committed to
OL,8,Fproviding an update to the Patient
OL,9,FSafety Commissioner at the earliest
OL,10,Fopportunity."
OL,12,FAn interim award of #25,000 was the
OL,13,F"median amount patients said would be
OL,14,Fappropriate", the Commissioner said.
OL,15,FThis would be followed by a main
OL,16,Fscheme with payouts based on the
OL,17,Findividual needs of each patient.
