OL,4,Cscandals 'ignored' by government
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, Dr Henrietta
OL,7,FHughes said: "I think there are
OL,8,Fconcerns about the size, the scale,
OL,9,Fbut also the uncertainty of the
OL,10,Fnumbers that might be harm, and that's
OL,11,Fwhy I set out a two-stage redress
OL,12,Fprocess.
OL,14,F"There's a big difference between warm
OL,15,Fwords to patients and money landing in
OL,16,Ftheir accounts and I think the
OL,17,FGovernment, and the previous
OL,18,FGovernment, have struggled with how to
OL,19,Fsquare that.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
