OL,3,CSurvivors of 'horrendous' medical
OL,4,Cscandals 'ignored' by government
OL,6,F"They can clearly see the suffering,
OL,7,Fthey can clearly see the case for
OL,8,Fredress, but there's also a practical
OL,9,Faspect to this which is how to turn
OL,10,Fthat into a sensible plan."
OL,12,FProfessor Henrietta Hughes spoke to
OL,13,FPolitical Correspondent Lise McNally
OL,14,Fto mark the anniversary of her report,
OL,15,Fsharing why there is still the need
OL,16,Ffor urgent action, and how she feels
OL,17,Fabout the delay.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
