OL,6,FJanet Williams, from Lancashire, and
OL,7,FEmma Murphy, from Greater Manchester,
OL,8,Fdesperately want to see action from
OL,9,Fthe government after both raising
OL,10,Fdisabled children who were exposed to
OL,11,FSodium Valproate.
OL,13,FThey prescribed the treatment when
OL,14,Fthey were pregnant.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
