OL,4,Cscandals 'ignored' by government
OL,6,FThe mums have campaigned for
OL,7,Fcompensation for victims, delivering
OL,8,Fmultiple letters to Downing Street to
OL,9,Furgie the Prime Minister to honour the
OL,10,Freport's recommendations.
OL,12,F"The families are always waiting and
OL,13,Fwe shouldn't have to wait," Emma said.
OL,14,F"We have proven that the government
OL,15,Fwas at fault. The government knew this
OL,16,Fmedicine would harm babies in utero
OL,17,Fand they ignored that."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
