OL,6,FShe added: "The warm words from MPs
OL,7,Fneed to stop. You're just continuing
OL,8,Fto insult our families and our
OL,9,Fchildren. We want action now."
OL,11,FJanet said: "At some point this has
OL,12,Fgot to stop. These families have to be
OL,13,Fcompensated."
OL,15,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,16,Fspokesperson said: "The harm caused by
OL,17,Fsodium valproate and pelvic mesh
OL,18,Fcontinues to be felt today.
