OL,6,F"Our sympathies are with those
OL,7,Faffected and we are fully focused on
OL,8,Fhow best to support patients and
OL,9,Fprevent future harm.
OL,11,F"This is a complex area of work and
OL,12,FHealth Minister Baroness Gillian
OL,13,FMerron met with some of those affected
OL,14,Fbefore Christmas, and has committed to
OL,15,Fproviding an update to the Patient
OL,16,FSafety Commissioner at the earliest
OL,17,Fopportunity."
